description: Deletes one or multiple versions of an annotation store.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the annotation store from which versions are being deleted.

parameters.name: versions
parameters.description: The versions of an annotation store to be deleted. (string) ---

nested_items.name: errors
nested_items.description: Any errors that occur when attempting to delete an annotation store version.

nested_items.name: versionName
nested_items.description: The name given to an annotation store version.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The message explaining the error in annotation store deletion.
